56.6929133858267775 600.907001952755877 Td
(\\text{BCE} = -\\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left[ y_i \\log\(\\hat{y}_i\) + \(1 - y_i\) \\log\(1 - \\hat{y}_i\)) Tj
